data.description: Opportunity Knocks !!!! The Best neighborhood of Palmdale, this captivating Single Family Residence at 37545 Ebony Drive, Palmdale, CA 93551-6144, offers a perfect blend of comfort and modern living. Built in 2015, this two-story residence  Solar paid!!!! Energy efficiency is a highlight.As you step into this home, you are welcomed by a spacious and unfurnished interior. With four bedrooms and three bathrooms, including three full baths, enormous laundry room,dinning area & Kitchen with center island, granite countertops,this residence spans approximately 2,370 square feet, providing ample space for relaxation and entertainment. Loft  is a large room perfect for kids game room or gym.The architectural beauty of this home is complemented by its two levels, adding a dynamic dimension to the living space.  Downstairs features  one bedroom and a full bath.Currently occupied by its owner, the property ensures a well-maintained and cared-for environment. custom window coverings with remote control.The neighborhood Anaverde Park with basketball and baseball court. playground & events for familys and kids for easter time, christmas and summer movies. The exterior of the property boasts a picturesque mountain view. The lot size is approximately 5,282 square feet, featuring a well-maintained backyard with block fence.Don't miss the chance to call this West Palmdale treasure your own..!!
